lead_paragraph: Andres Iniesta's injury comeback cannot arrive soon enough for Barcelona who head into the first 'El Clasico' of the season on Saturday trailing La Liga leaders Real Madrid by six points.

headline.print_headline: Iniesta's Potential Return a Boost for Barca
